subject: resource/WFLZ-FM
object: WFLZ-FM (93.3 FM, "93-3 FLZ")  is a CHR/Pop station broadcasting in the Tampa Bay area, Florida, USA. The station has a class C signal operating at 100,000 watts effective radiated power, and is one of the most powerful FM radio stations in Florida, covering four of the state's radio markets.  The station's studios are located in South Tampa and the transmitter site is in Riverview.WFLZ currently broadcasts in HD format.  93.3 HD-1 simulcasts the analog WFLZ-FM 93.3 MHz ("93-3 FLZ HD-1 Hit music"), whereas 93.3 HD-2 exclusively broadcasts dance music ("Evolution on 93-3 FLZ HD-2").
